---
title: Thai Spiced Salmon & Roast Pumpkin Wedges with Cucumber Salad & Sweet Chilli Lemon Dressing
description: Bursting with bold Thai-inspired flavours and vibrant pumpkin, this surprisingly simple salmon dish is not your average weeknight meal.

*This recipe is under 650kcal per serving.*
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/thai-spiced-salmon-roast-pumpkin-wedges-ff5fabe1.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.co.nz/recipecards/card/thai-spiced-salmon-roast-pumpkin-wedges-615fda8c78c5104dd5312d1f-3180e892.pdf
